(4. HOW THE APP STARTS) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(`SRC/MAIN.JSX`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file mounts the React app into the browser page. It also connects the app to) Tj
T*
(Redux state.) Tj
T*
T*
(Key steps:) Tj
T*
(1. Load React and ReactDOM.) Tj
T*
(2. Import the Redux store from `src/store/store.js`.) Tj
T*
(3. Wrap the app in `<Provider store={store}>`.) Tj
T*
(4. Render `<App />` inside the HTML element with id `root`.) Tj
T*
T*
(`SRC/APP.JSX`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file defines the main page structure.) Tj
T*
T*
(Behavior:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Calls `useFirebaseSync\(\)` to load saved basket data and keep the basket saved on) Tj
T*
(every change.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Renders the page layout with two sections:) Tj
T*
(  - `<Products />` on the left) Tj
T*
(  - `<Basket />` on the right) Tj
T*
T*
(The overall layout is simple and responsive.) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(5. STATE MANAGEMENT WITH REDUX) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(`SRC/STORE/STORE.JS`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file creates the Redux store.) Tj
T*
T*
(It configures one reducer:) Tj
T*
