(‚ÄĘ `cart` managed by `cartSlice`) Tj
T*
T*
(`SRC/STORE/CARTSLICE.JS`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file defines the cart state and actions.) Tj
T*
T*
(State shape:) Tj
T*
({) Tj
T*
(  items: {},) Tj
T*
(}) Tj
T*
T*
(Each cart item is stored by product id, for example:) Tj
T*
({ bread: 2, cheese: 1 }) Tj
T*
T*
(Reducers:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `addItem\(id\)` ‚ÄĒ add one item or increase quantity) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `increaseQty\(id\)` ‚ÄĒ increase quantity) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `decreaseQty\(id\)` ‚ÄĒ decrease quantity or remove item) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `clearCart\(\)` ‚ÄĒ empty the basket) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `setCart\(items\)` ‚ÄĒ replace the whole cart with saved data) Tj
T*
T*
(This makes cart operations fast and simple.) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(6. PRODUCT LOADING AND DISPLAY) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(`SRC/COMPONENTS/PRODUCTS.JSX`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This component loads the product list and renders it.) Tj
T*
T*
(Behavior:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Uses `useState` to hold products.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Uses `useEffect` to load products when the component mounts.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Calls `getProducts\(\)` from `src/firebase/productService.js`.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Displays each product with the `<ProductItem />` component.) Tj
T*
T*
(`SRC/FIREBASE/PRODUCTSERVICE.JS`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file decides where product data comes from.) Tj
T*
T*
(Behavior:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ If Firebase is configured, fetch products from Firestore.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ If Firebase is not configured or fails, load static product data from) Tj
T*
(`src/data/products.js`.) Tj
T*
T*
(This means the app works even if Firebase is not set up.) Tj
T*
T*
(`SRC/COMPONENTS/PRODUCTITEM.JSX`) Tj
T*
T*
ET
