T*
(‚ÄĘ product name) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ product price) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ an `Add` button) Tj
T*
T*
(When the user clicks `Add`, it dispatches `addItem\(product.id\)` to Redux.) Tj
T*
T*
