T*
T*
(7. BASKET DISPLAY AND USER ACTIONS) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(`SRC/COMPONENTS/BASKET.JSX`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This component shows the current basket and totals.) Tj
T*
T*
(Behavior:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Reads `cartItems` from Redux using `useSelector`.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Calls `calculateBill\(cartItems\)` to compute pricing, discounts, and totals.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Shows each item using `<BasketItem />`.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Displays subtotal, savings, and total.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Adds a `Clear all` button when there are items.) Tj
T*
T*
(`SRC/COMPONENTS/BASKETITEM.JSX`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This component shows one item in the basket.) Tj
T*
T*
(It displays:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ product name) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ unit price) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ quantity controls \(+ / -\)) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ subtotal for that line) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ savings for that item) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ final cost for that line) Tj
T*
T*
(The buttons dispatch `increaseQty` and `decreaseQty` actions.) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(8. CALCULATING THE BILL AND DISCOUNTS) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(`SRC/UTILS/CALCULATEBILL.JS`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file contains the core pricing logic.) Tj
T*
T*
(It performs three steps:) Tj
T*
(1. Build a line-by-line summary for every product in the cart.) Tj
T*
