(2. Apply discount offers.) Tj
T*
(3. Return subtotal, savings, total, and item details.) Tj
T*
T*
(DISCOUNT RULES IN THIS APP) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(The app supports these offers:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `Cheese` ‚ÄĒ buy one, get one free) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `Soup + Bread` ‚ÄĒ each soup makes one bread half price) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `Butter` ‚ÄĒ 33% off) Tj
T*
T*
(HOW IT WORKS) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(For each product in the cart:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ compute `unitPrice` and `lineSubtotal`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ add that data to the breakdown object) Tj
T*
T*
(Then apply each offer function:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `applyCheeseBogof\(\)`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `applySoupBreadOffer\(\)`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `applyButterDiscount\(\)`) Tj
T*
T*
(Each offer updates the line totals and records the saving.) Tj
T*
T*
(Finally, the function returns:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `subtotal`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `appliedOffers`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `totalSavings`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `total`) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ `items` for display) Tj
T*
T*
(This is how the basket shows both normal costs and discount savings.) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(9. OPTIONAL FIREBASE BASKET SYNC) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(`SRC/HOOKS/USEFIREBASESYNC.JS`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This hook keeps the cart synchronized with Firestore.) Tj
T*
T*
(Behavior:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ On first render, call `loadBasket\(\)` to load saved cart data.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ If saved cart data exists, dispatch `setCart\(savedCart\)`.) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ Every time the cart changes, call `saveBasket\(cartItems\)`.) Tj
T*
T*
(`SRC/FIREBASE/SAVEBASKET.JS`) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(This file saves and loads the basket from Firestore.) Tj
T*
T*
ET
