T*
(That makes the cart feel persistent across browser reloads.) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(10. HOW THE USER INTERACTS WITH THE APP) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(1. Open the web app in the browser.) Tj
T*
(2. The product list loads.) Tj
T*
(3. Click `Add` on a product to put it into the basket.) Tj
T*
(4. The basket updates immediately.) Tj
T*
(5. Use `+` and `-` inside the basket to change quantities.) Tj
T*
(6. Discounts appear automatically in the totals.) Tj
T*
(7. If Firebase is enabled, the basket saves automatically.) Tj
T*
T*
(These steps are handled by React UI components, Redux state, and the billing logic.) Tj
T*
T*
