T*
(npm run dev) Tj
T*
T*
(Open `http://localhost:5173` in the browser.) Tj
T*
T*
(Run tests:) Tj
T*
T*
(npm test) Tj
T*
T*
(---) Tj
T*
T*
(12. WHERE TO MAKE CHANGES) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(If you want to add a new product:) Tj
T*
(‚ÄĘ update `src/data/products.js`) Tj
T*
